tkcmd		Generic tk command interface with R syntax
tkwidget	Generic tk widget creation
.Tcl		Low-level interface to Tcl (execute  command string)
.Tcl.callback   Create Tcl callback from R function
.Tcl.args       Convert R argument list to Tcl options
tk.start        Init Tcl interpreter and start Tk event handling
tk.stop         Stop Tk event handling

--- Widget creation ---
tkbutton        Create button widget
<etc>

--- Widget commands ---
tkconfigure     Widget configuration
<etc>

--- Other commands ---
tkbind          Event binding

tkpack          Geometry manager

[There's a huge number of commands. Use Tk documentation for details.]
